    "en": {
      "title": "Former President Gotabha is allowed to stay in Singapore for another 02 weeks",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the Singaporean authorities have decided to allow former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to stay in Singapore for another two weeks.",
        "Accordingly, former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has been allowed to stay in the country until August 11.",
        "Former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa went to Singapore on last July 14th from Maldives in a plane belonging to Saudi Airlines."
      ],
